" ---------- Plugins ----------

" ========== NerdTREE ==========
"Toggle NerdTREE
map <F2> :NERDTreeToggle<CR>

" ========= Expand Selection =========
vmap v <Plug>(expand_region_expand)
vmap <C-v> <Plug>(expand_region_shrink)

nmap <Leader>f <Plug>CtrlSFPrompt

"Integration to system's clipboard
map <Leader>y "*y<CR>
map <Leader>p "*p<CR>

"Open command output
nmap <leader>h :!<CR>
